This package contains a number of helper classes for interacting with monitor entries ing Ping Identity, UnboundID, and Alcatel-Lucent 8661 server products.

Package com.unboundid.ldap.sdk.unboundidds.monitors Description

This package contains a number of helper classes for interacting with monitor entries ing Ping Identity, UnboundID, and Alcatel-Lucent 8661 server products. It provides methods for parsing the monitor entries as specific subtypes and for extracting the information that they provide in useful ways.
NOTE: The classes within this package, and elsewhere within the com.unboundid.ldap.sdk.unboundidds package structure, are only supported for use against Ping Identity, UnboundID, and Alcatel-Lucent 8661 server products. These classes provide support for proprietary functionality or for external specifications that are not considered stable or mature enough to be guaranteed to work in an interoperable way with other types of LDAP servers.

The MonitorManager class provides a number of utility methods for retrieving server monitor entries from a Ping Identity/UnboundID Directory Server. The MonitorEntry class and its subclasses provide access to the data in those monitor entries.
